query:
INSERT INTO places (atollId, name, code, type)
SELECT 
  COALESCE((SELECT id FROM atolls LIMIT 1), 1),
  ml.name,
  LOWER(REPLACE(ml.slug, '-', '_')),
  'airport'
FROM map_locations ml
WHERE ml.name LIKE '%airport%' OR ml.name LIKE '%gan%'
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE type = 'airport'
